\v 6 I'm astounded that you \add people\add* have so quicklyÂŠ125638 replaced the goodÂŠ125650 messageÂŠ125650 \add that you heard\add* from the one who calledÂŠ125642 you to the \nd messiah\nd*'s graceÂŠ125646. You've replaced it with anotherÂŠ125649 narrative
