\v 10 Am I trying to please and persuadeÂŠ125708 people or \nd GodÂŠ125712\nd*? If I was stillÂŠ125719 trying to please people, I wouldn't be \add worthy to be\add* one of the \nd messiah\nd*'s slavesÂŠ125723.
