\v 11 I'm letting you know, brothersÂŠ125731 andÂŠ125731 sistersÂŠ125731, thatÂŠ125738 the good message I proclaimed didn'tÂŠ125744 just come from humanÂŠ125747 ideas.
\v 12 It didn't come from my ideas, nor was I taughtÂŠ125757 it by some other person, but it was revealed to me by \nd Yeshua\nd* the \nd messiahÂŠ125762\nd*.
