\v 14 I was progressingÂŠ125784 in JudaismÂŠ125787\x + \xo 1:14: \xt Acts 22:3.\x* quicker than many of myÂŠ125794 contemporariesÂŠ125790, beingÂŠ125798 so much more zealousÂŠ125797 in observing our ancient traditionsÂŠ125802.
