\v 16 so that he could revealÂŠ125822 hisÂŠ125825 son through me, and I could preachÂŠ125829 the goodÂŠ125829 messageÂŠ125829 to non-Jews. I didn'tÂŠ125836 rush to get advice from others,
\v 17 nor did I head to Yerushalem to \add consult with\add* the ambassadorsÂŠ125851 there that preceded me, butÂŠ125856 I went away to ArabiaÂŠ125855 and then later returnedÂŠ125858 to DamascusÂŠ125860.
