\p
\v 1 It was fourteenÂŠ125953 yearsÂŠ125954 later that I made the uphill trek to Yerushalem\x + \xo 2:1: \xt Acts 11:30; 15:2.\x* with BarnabasÂŠ125961, taking TitosÂŠ125965 alongÂŠ125963 as well.
