\p
\v 1 You foolishÂŠ126367 GalatiansÂŠ126368, who tricked youÂŠ126370 into changing? You know that \nd Yeshua\nd* the \nd messiahÂŠ126380\nd* was publiclyÂŠ126381 known to have been executedÂŠ126384 \add by being nailed to\add*\x + \xo 3:1: \xt Jhn 20:25.\x* a post.
