\v 3 So aren't you being foolishÂŠ126403? HavingÂŠ126405 begunÂŠ126405 in the \nd spiritÂŠ126406\nd*, now you \add people\add* are focussing back on bodily discipline.
\v 4 You vainly endured so many thingsâit was vain wasn't it?
\v 5 SoÂŠ126419 the one who gave the \nd spiritÂŠ126423\nd* to you and worked miraclesÂŠ126426 amongÂŠ126427 you, did all that come about from obeying the rules or by the faithÂŠ126438 that came from hearingÂŠ126437 \add the good message\add*?
