\v 16 The promisesÂŠ126621 were given to AbrahamÂŠ126618 andÂŠ126622 to hisÂŠ126625 offspring. It doesn't say âoffsprings (plural)â butÂŠ126634 is only referring to the one who's the \nd messiahÂŠ126644\nd*.
