\p
\v 1 ButÂŠ126872 as longÂŠ126874 as the heir is underage, he's no wealthier than a slaveÂŠ126882 (even though he'll \add become\add* the masterÂŠ126883),
\v 2 butÂŠ126890 he's underÂŠ126887 guardiansÂŠ126888 and managersÂŠ126891 untilÂŠ126892 he reaches the age that his fatherÂŠ126897 specified.
