\v 4 butÂŠ126913 at the appointed timeÂŠ126918, \nd GodÂŠ126921\nd* sentÂŠ126919 hisÂŠ126924 son down to be given birth to by a womanÂŠ126927 and to live underÂŠ126929 \add Mosheh's\add* law
