\v 6 SoÂŠ126941 becauseÂŠ126940 you're now children, \nd GodÂŠ126946\nd* sent hisÂŠ126951 son's \nd spiritÂŠ126948\nd* down into ourÂŠ126955 heartsÂŠ126954 as we call out, âFather, father.â
