\p
\v 17 Those \add others\add* have worked hard to \add try to win\add* you \add over\add*, but not for good \add reasons\add*âthey want to cut you off so that you'll be enthusiastic about them.
\v 18 It's good to be enthusiastic about things that are alwaysÂŠ127124 good, and not only at the times when I'm with you, \add brothers and sisters\add*.
\v 19 MyÂŠ127136 dear ones, who I'm againÂŠ127138 labouringÂŠ127139 with in childbirth untilÂŠ127140 the \nd messiahÂŠ127144\nd* becomes part of youÂŠ127146,
